title: Bug 114470 [Smoke] Error message throws when using new Date('3/2/2005') as value in table filter.
description: When using the expression 'new Date('3/2/2005')' as a value in a table filter, an error message is thrown.
EB: After saving and previewing the report, the filter should work without errors.
SR:
1. Open the report that contains a table with a filter.
2. Set the filter value to 'new Date('3/2/2005')'.
3. Save the report.
4. Preview the report.
5. Verify that the filter works without errors.
